Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.80,0:00:09.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…在那裡嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.85,0:00:26.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體無法隨心所欲…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.96,0:00:30.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不聽使喚…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.56,0:00:37.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一騎 去感覺法夫那的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.50,0:00:38.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和他融為一體！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.77,0:01:22.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總士 今天也聽得到嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.21,0:01:24.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.61,0:01:26.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交給我修理就沒問題囉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.48,0:01:29.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又來了 你是說真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.78,0:01:30.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.29,0:01:33.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…在那裡嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.16,0:01:36.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是真的耶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.63,0:01:38.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要回答看看嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.79,0:01:40.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.46,0:01:42.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,預備…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.78,0:02:35.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樂園 - 開始
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.74,0:03:29.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出門了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.25,0:03:43.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真矢呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.58,0:03:45.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她已經出去囉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.15,0:03:46.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是社團的晨間練習嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.92,0:03:49.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她說過今天沒有練習
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.22,0:03:51.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是去羽佐間同學家了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.80,0:03:59.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翔子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.17,0:04:00.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真矢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.60,0:04:02.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.74,0:04:05.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天可以去嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.18,0:04:11.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以進去嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.88,0:04:12.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請進
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.82,0:04:16.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天妳走了之後 我就被媽媽罵了一頓
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.05,0:04:18.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.25,0:04:22.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她擔心真矢會因為我而遲到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.06,0:04:24.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.39,0:04:26.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一小段路衝刺一下就到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.89,0:04:28.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要把這種事放在心上啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.70,0:04:30.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真矢…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.57,0:04:36.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 看來妳比昨天有精神
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.71,0:04:38.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.08,0:04:44.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.08,0:04:49.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.65,0:04:52.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要咲良要到學校去上課了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.52,0:04:55.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.66,0:05:01.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.01,0:05:19.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.81,0:05:21.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以翔子呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.55,0:05:22.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是沒辦法來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.75,0:05:23.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.62,0:05:27.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過她一定很快就會好起來的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.69,0:05:28.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說得也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.90,0:05:34.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.56,0:05:37.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.13,0:05:38.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個就拜託你囉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.97,0:05:41.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這本書非常重要喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.54,0:05:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.02,0:06:38.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是今天早上回來的嗎 總士
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.09,0:06:43.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我在CDC打報告 所以回來得晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.97,0:06:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各方面都辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.47,0:06:50.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學到了不少東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.72,0:07:06.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的夕陽顏色似乎會很特別
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.93,0:07:17.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對 不是那樣的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.93,0:07:21.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 我沒有注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.17,0:07:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皆城同學 你回來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.57,0:07:25.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 我剛回來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.81,0:07:28.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.18,0:07:30.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總士 歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.88,0:07:33.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道那是最新的一集？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.58,0:07:35.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我等好久囉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.08,0:07:38.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皆城 東京很好玩嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.45,0:07:40.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,東京？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.09,0:07:44.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實也沒什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.66,0:07:47.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有碰到什麼藝人之類的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.76,0:07:48.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.76,0:07:50.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.33,0:07:52.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一騎呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.47,0:07:55.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他一下課就跟近藤同學出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.78,0:08:03.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總士已經回來了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.18,0:08:10.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來沒辦法再來我家玩了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.46,0:08:19.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就到此為止
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.29,0:08:20.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先走啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.80,0:08:22.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 一騎！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.40,0:08:25.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛那是什麼感覺？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.17,0:08:34.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在那裡嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.49,0:08:45.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被發現了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.81,0:09:05.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.01,0:09:07.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是春日井甲洋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.58,0:09:09.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確認
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.21,0:09:12.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.85,0:09:14.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 你們先自習吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.85,0:09:16.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自習？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.25,0:09:18.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是還有人沒來…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.25,0:09:20.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係 他們在別的避難所
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.36,0:09:22.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.62,0:09:24.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是亞爾維斯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.83,0:09:28.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有系統全部上線
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.36,0:09:30.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生命體振動波確認 立即傳送
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.36,0:09:32.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目標質量增加中
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.77,0:09:34.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是人面獅身型嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.77,0:09:35.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所羅門呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.87,0:09:37.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尚未起動
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.47,0:09:39.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用質量測定搜索敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.67,0:09:43.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發佈紅色警戒 執行第三種戰鬥配置
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.11,0:09:45.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全員進行第三種戰鬥配置
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.01,0:09:47.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備展開波動屏障
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.88,0:09:49.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解除偽裝鏡面
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.02,0:09:53.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 那邊沒有避難所的入口
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.29,0:09:54.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.17,0:10:05.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太陽被…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.31,0:10:14.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偽裝鏡面解除完畢 開啟第一波動屏障
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.94,0:10:17.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居民全部疏散完了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.81,0:10:21.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已確定93.7%的居民疏散完成
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.32,0:10:22.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儘速準備迎擊！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.82,0:10:25.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藍色大地部隊 請盡快出發
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.45,0:10:28.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道 大家都準備好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.19,0:10:29.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再20秒就可以出發
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.06,0:10:31.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.96,0:10:33.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心點喔 親愛的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.00,0:10:35.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.53,0:10:38.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確定對方為敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.30,0:10:40.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藍色大地部隊 出發
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.94,0:10:50.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翔子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.85,0:10:51.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真矢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.45,0:10:53.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真矢…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.45,0:10:57.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底發生什麼事情 怎麼連小酷都逃走了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.59,0:11:01.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小酷一定躲到安全的地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.56,0:11:03.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也趕快去避難吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.26,0:11:08.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目標接觸第一波動屏障
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.96,0:11:10.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輸出功率降低 要被突破了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.20,0:11:13.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啟動集群防禦系統
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.88,0:11:25.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集群防禦系統啟動完成
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.61,0:11:27.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目標繼續前進中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.35,0:11:29.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目標進入肉眼可辨識的範圍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.08,0:11:31.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將傳送到螢幕上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.40,0:11:44.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是異界體…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.79,0:12:13.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是異界體…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.66,0:12:15.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 並不是這樣的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.80,0:12:20.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,單體密度2.33 原子量28.0855
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.67,0:12:23.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陰性度1.8 質量固定
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.34,0:12:25.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,異界體即將實體化
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.18,0:12:32.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.95,0:12:37.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美麗並不代表會是人類的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.45,0:12:39.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一波動屏障的負荷上昇中
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.82,0:12:42.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有75%的機率會在十秒內與敵人的頻率同調
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.06,0:12:44.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目標確認
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.56,0:12:46.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所預測位置的誤差20
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.06,0:12:49.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屏障一解除便展開攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.70,0:12:55.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分成兩組攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.87,0:12:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靶子這麼大 沒打中的不准吃晚飯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.71,0:12:59.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家上！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.55,0:13:13.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒打中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.56,0:13:15.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行動被猜到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.00,0:13:22.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有人快離開
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.60,0:13:23.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.10,0:13:37.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…在那裡嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.12,0:13:46.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目標從上空接近第二波動屏障
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.63,0:13:57.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們會變成怎樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.90,0:14:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怕什麼 有點骨氣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.54,0:14:05.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羽佐間她們不會有事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.01,0:14:13.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.52,0:14:18.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以待在那種地方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.05,0:14:21.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點躲進亞爾維斯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.46,0:14:22.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞爾維斯？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.06,0:14:24.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.93,0:14:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.77,0:14:40.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣…為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.23,0:15:02.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向島的自律迎擊系統被消滅了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.33,0:15:05.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是棘手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.83,0:15:10.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今只能讓那個巨人覺醒了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.97,0:15:15.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備進入法夫那啟動階段
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.84,0:15:16.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,駕駛員呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.84,0:15:19.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在正搭乘電磁彈艙往停機庫移動中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.22,0:15:23.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.62,0:15:24.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.32,0:15:29.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的兒子也曾經駕駛法夫那喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.72,0:15:32.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以妳也加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.03,0:15:34.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.51,0:15:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電磁彈艙信號於龍宮島南方250公尺附近消失
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.21,0:15:53.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,駕駛員以及工作人員一名目前生死不明
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.38,0:15:54.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.88,0:15:57.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目標正前往法夫那機庫
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.02,0:16:00.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打算先破壞巨人是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.35,0:16:02.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啟動剛瑠島上的EPM
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.79,0:16:05.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儘可能阻止它的前進
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.63,0:16:16.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,系統準備完畢 發射EPM
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.58,0:16:22.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已捕捉到目標
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.04,0:16:25.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸 我來駕駛法夫那吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.91,0:16:26.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總士
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.82,0:16:31.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些事只有你才做得到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.96,0:16:36.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,齊格飛系統…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.36,0:16:43.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以吧 總士
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.43,0:16:46.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.00,0:16:49.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛瑠島EPM 再兩分鐘之後到達極限
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.70,0:16:52.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女神之巖的情況呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.17,0:16:54.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有反應
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.41,0:16:56.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是沒辦法嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.71,0:17:01.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儘快準備迎擊用的反戰車飛彈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.12,0:17:05.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多撐一分鐘 甚至一秒鐘就好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.05,0:17:08.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真壁 可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.66,0:17:12.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是現階段的最適合人選
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.79,0:17:14.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要用他了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.54,0:17:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總士…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.87,0:17:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們…要去哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.98,0:17:38.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去樂園
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.05,0:17:42.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,EPM輸出功率降低
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.53,0:17:46.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.76,0:17:48.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是法夫那
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.26,0:17:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法夫那？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.76,0:17:54.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳說中為了保護寶藏 而化身為龍的巨人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.17,0:17:56.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼承這個巨人之名而研發 以對抗異界體的機體
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.07,0:18:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要防止異界體的讀心能力 唯有以法夫那與其對抗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.28,0:18:06.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你以它來守護這座島吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.98,0:18:09.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能 我辦不到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.55,0:18:11.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 你辦得到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.95,0:18:16.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定知道 你的身體可以跟法夫那合為一體
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.13,0:18:23.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今要守護這座島 只能仰賴法夫那了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.93,0:18:28.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果可以的話我也想去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.14,0:18:30.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.04,0:18:36.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今能辦得到的人只有你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.31,0:18:40.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的辦得到嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.78,0:18:44.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.49,0:18:53.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法夫那Mark XI 單機作戰準備出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.56,0:18:56.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,NO.11巨龍之洞準備開啟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.16,0:18:59.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進入齊格飛系統
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.67,0:19:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總士
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.27,0:19:03.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.77,0:19:05.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.08,0:19:16.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真壁一騎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.58,0:19:17.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真了不起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.82,0:19:20.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照這個數值看來不穿協同作用服也沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.66,0:19:25.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.26,0:19:28.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.90,0:19:31.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-加油吧\N-好的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.37,0:19:37.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一騎 準備好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.64,0:19:40.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啟動尼貝龍根吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.31,0:19:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尼貝龍根…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.12,0:19:51.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認得…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.62,0:19:55.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認得它
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.04,0:20:10.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輸入對數螺旋形成
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.14,0:20:11.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進行協同線路認證
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.91,0:20:15.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尼貝龍根啟動確認 連接齊格飛系統
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.88,0:20:18.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法夫那Mark XI 準備出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.65,0:20:21.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.38,0:20:23.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是第三機庫
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.35,0:20:26.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武器運輸用的密碼被鎖定了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.89,0:20:29.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要使用武器必須用生體解除鑰匙來解除
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.56,0:20:31.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣法夫那不就手無寸鐵了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.49,0:20:32.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我馬上過去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.83,0:20:36.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真壁 之後就交給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.94,0:20:44.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一騎 一騎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.41,0:20:50.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總士 你怎麼會在這裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.71,0:20:54.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在是直接進入你的大腦視聽區
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.41,0:20:57.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在法夫那體內的你以及在齊格飛裡面的我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.58,0:21:01.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼此的大腦皮質神經細胞處於直接連結的狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.89,0:21:05.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過沒有協同作用服 所以連結狀態並不完全
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.16,0:21:11.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今最重要的是讓你和法夫那合為一體
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.77,0:21:12.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先張開你的眼睛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.13,0:21:14.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼睛？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.17,0:21:17.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 法夫那的眼睛就是你的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.94,0:21:23.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.24,0:21:26.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 那傢伙快來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.71,0:21:29.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開啟NO.11巨龍之洞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.22,0:21:32.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法夫那Mark XI 出動！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.55,0:21:36.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的旅程就這樣開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.23,0:21:41.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我們能夠僥倖生還
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.06,0:21:45.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,願我們不會忘記至今的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.80,0:21:51.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到將來這座島嶼恢復為原本樂園的那天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
